<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_0f1dcea2-0a18-4bcb-b9b6-fb7ef09443c7" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><sptc>G1F5</sptc><title id="_4cfc2bf5-8a28-4407-9eb1-e13eb62e39e1">Cleaning of windows</title><subclause id="_2a7d75ba-8d08-4869-be09-dc575d4050fe" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_15d2b797-e6b2-452d-bee3-271786082b26">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building is to be provided with a means to allow for the safe cleaning of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1525_29.1.0.xml#_48631093-d96b-4a40-a86d-7ffae028f24d" id="_d1184438-6131-46d3-919e-fdd9dc17440f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">windows</xref>.</p></subclause><callout id="_7499ef69-667e-4a27-bb25-b681b0128acb"><callout-type ncc-info-type="application"/><p>NSW G1F5 only applies where any <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1525_29.1.0.xml#_48631093-d96b-4a40-a86d-7ffae028f24d" id="_d1000cd4-8c6c-4567-8a54-d1bec3536e26" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">windows</xref> are located 3 or more <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_8e5e45a6-2b74-48fb-8469-f5aea4c13f2f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storeys</xref> above ground level.</p></callout></clause>